data.description: AC 2022 & 2016. Roof and water heaters 7 yrs  unique/one of a kind, updated and extended. Upon entering, you're greeted by the convenience of a powder room right by the entrance, making freshening up a breeze for both residents and guests. To the right, a dedicated theater room, setting the stage for thrilling movie nights with family and friends. The gourmet kitchen features a convenient pot filler, an extra-large farmhouse sink, and an abundance of cabinet space. Luxurious master suite with the custom-made master closet. It's a paradise for anyone seeking the ultimate in organization. Guesthouse with a bed, bath and a game room above Garage, an inviting retreat for guests . A fully-equipped kitchenette for added convenience. Ample carport ensuring your vehicles stay in pristine condition. Electric Vehicle (EV)/RV charging capabilities. Stay eco-conscious with this convenient feature.
